</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_341" id="169v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Dem vesten Görgen von Grunbach </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab><app>
<note place="margin">
<expan>S<ex>i</ex>n<ex>e</ex></expan>
<expan>s<ex>er</ex>vicio.</expan>
</note>
</app>Görg von Grunbach, als ir uns <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt
                        von der gebawr <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> zu Grassulcz, die
                                <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Ryet<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, zusteen, wie ir ir veynd
                                <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> seyt und wie sie ewch und
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>knechte<ex>n</ex></expan> etwas <expan>v<ex>er</ex>driess</expan>
                        getan sülle <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> etc., das
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu
                        ist uns vor <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> niht wissend
                                <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan>, so seyn wir auch von ewch noch von
                                <expan>niema<ex>n</ex>ts</expan> von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> vormals <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> keinrley
                        niht <expan>erynn<ex>er</ex>t</expan>
<expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan>. So <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir den
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Ryet<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> auch zu rede gesaczt, der hat uns gesagt, daz
                        im vor <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> auch niht wissend
                                <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> sey und ir kein recht von
                                <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>arme<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>lewt<ex>en</ex></expan> an in niht <expan>geford<ex>er</ex>t</expan>
                        noch begert habt. <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>hette<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ewch niht getrawt, daz ir
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>arme<ex>n</ex>lewte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>unerford<ex>er</ex>t</expan> alles <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        sölich <expan>schede<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>zugeczog<ex>en</ex></expan> hett und <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        ewch noch und <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, daz ir dem
                                <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>arme<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>lewt<ex>en</ex></expan>, das ir daz ir in
                            <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> habt, <expan>wid<ex>er</ex>keret</expan>
                        und die <expan>gefang<ex>en</ex></expan> ledig lasset. Hett ir denn zu
                                <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>arme<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>lewte<ex>n</ex></expan> icht <expan>zuspreche<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> mugt ir sie mit recht
                                <expan>fürwente<ex>n</ex></expan> an die gericht darein sie gehörn,
                        hett ir <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> zu dem
                            <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<pb facs="#facs_342" id="170r"/>
<expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Ryet<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, icht <expan>zuspreche<ex>n</ex></expan>, so
                                <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ewch <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>scheinbott<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> vollen
                        gwalt <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> slewnigs
                            <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>helff<ex>en</ex></expan> vor des reichs
                            <expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns zu
                            <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>
<expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lichen</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>Symo<ex>n</ex>is</expan> et Jude. </ab></div>
